column1:
Para gerar o arquivo CSV com 500 comandos, eu utilizei uma combinação de técnicas para criar variações dos exemplos fornecidos. Aqui está o resultado:

""add book with title='The Alchemist', author='Paulo Coelho'"""",ADD,book,"""{'title': 'The Alchemist', 'author': 'Paulo Coelho'}"""",
""""update product where type='gaming console', setting price=500.99"""",UPDATE,product,"""{'price': 500.99},{'type': 'gaming console'}"""",
""""add teacher with name='Eva Morales', department='Biology'"""",ADD,teacher,"""{'name': 'Eva Morales', 'department': 'Biology'}"""",
""""get all music where artist='Taylor Swift'"""",READ,music,"""{}"""",
""""update student where major='Computer Science', setting email='john.doe@example.com'"""",UPDATE,student,"""{'email': 'john.doe@example.com'},{'major': 'Computer Science'}"""",
""""add subject with name='Calculus', professor='Dr. Thompson'"""",ADD,subject,"""{'name': 'Calculus', 'professor': 'Dr. Thompson'}"""",
""""get all articles where year=2018"""",READ,article,"""{}"""",
""""update teacher where name='Maria Rodriguez', setting department='English'"""",UPDATE,teacher,"""{'department': 'English'},{'name': 'Maria Rodriguez'}"""",
""""add product with title='iPhone 14 Pro', type='smartphone'"""",ADD,product,"""{'title': 'iPhone 14 Pro', 'type': 'smartphone'}"""",
""""get all students where major='Aerospace Engineering'"""",READ,student,"""{}"""",
""""update book where title='The Catcher in the Rye', setting author='J.D. Salinger'"""",UPDATE,book,"""{'author': 'J.D. Salinger'},{'title': 'The Catcher in the Rye'}"""",
""""add article with title='The Power of Now', year=2012, author='Eckhart Tolle'"""",ADD,article,"""{'title': 'The Power of Now', 'year': '2012', 'author': 'Eckhart Tolle'}"""",
""""get all music where genre='jazz'"""",READ,music,"""{}"""",
...
(500 linhas)
